race.description: Ladbrokes Spring Hosted Pots Mdn Plate
race.comment: OXIDIZE (7) lifted strongly only to just miss first-up over 1120m at this track. Should tighten right up following that outing and has more up her sleeve. Races forward and will be hard to beat. CAN'T CATCH CHILLI (10) led here second-up from an inside gate and was beaten 1L over this trip. She's an improved galloper who will jump and run from the paint. Presents fitter again and can go one better with Darmanin going on. LA ZAMPA (1) was beaten 1L in the OXIDIZE race, improving again. Has a wide gate but peaks and can make the finish with average luck. ZIGGY PLAYS GUITAR (3) was having his first outing for the new barn in the same contest. The former was beaten 2.3L and should be better for it. In the mix. SURF SOUL (2) resumes and has switched from a smart Victorian stable. May need one, but he has some ability and will be naturally improved.
